                      usb_hcd_irq+0x26/0x40 [usbcore]
                      irq_forced_thread_fn+0x2f/0x70
                      irq_thread+0x149/0x1d0
                      kthread+0x113/0x150
                      ret_from_fork+0x2e/0x40

This patch fixes the problem.

